videos.headline: Virginia QB follows blocks for 23-yard TD run
videos.description: Bryce Perkins slams through the hole and follows his blockers for a 23-yard touchdown on the opening drive.

videos.headline: UVA's Perkins stretches for 3-yard TD
videos.description: Bryce Perkins escapes the pocket and reaches for the pylon run on a 3-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Duke's Jones hits target in stride for 46-yard TD
videos.description: Daniel Jones tosses a 46-yard touchdown to Chris Taylor to get Duke on the board vs. Virginia.

videos.headline: UVA player acts his way to flag with major flop
videos.description: Virginia's Chuck Davis takes a page from Shakespeare and horribly flops for an extra 15 yards.
